1. Danas imam dva *sastanka* u kancelariji. (Today I have two meetings in the office.)
2. Naš *sastanak* je odložen za sutra. (Our meeting has been postponed to tomorrow.)
3. Molim vas da zakazete *sastanak* sa direktorom. (Please schedule a meeting with the director.)
4. Ovaj *sastanak* će biti veoma važan za našu firmu. (This meeting will be very important for our company.)
5. Kolege su se srele na *sastanku* u restoranu. (Colleagues met at a meeting in a restaurant.)
6. Nadam se da će ovaj *sastanak* biti produktivan i da ćemo postići dogovor. (I hope this meeting will be productive and that we will reach an agreement.)
7. Da li imate predlog za dnevni red našeg *sastanka*? (Do you have a suggestion for the agenda of our meeting?)
8. Ovaj *sastanak* je zakazan za 14 časova. (This meeting is scheduled for 2 pm.)
9. Molim vas da se pridružite našem *sastanku* putem video poziva. (Please join our meeting via video call.)
10. Naš *sastanak* je trajao tri sata. (Our meeting lasted for three hours.)